efund will be made.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;4. The refund amount will be returned only after the event within 3 working days.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Itinerary of the event:-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Day 1 (2nd September 2017)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;I) Depart from Bangalore around 6AM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;II) Have Breakfast enroute&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;III)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;text_exposed_show&quot; style=&quot;display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Visit Manjarabad fort&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIV) Have Lunch enroute&lt;br /&gt;\r\nV) Reach Homestay&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVI) Freshen up and Get ready for Campfire&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVII) Enjoy the Campfire party and bonfire dinner&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVIII) End it all with staying in tents/dorms&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDay 2 (3rd September 2017)&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI) Have some Tea early in the morning and Leave for Trek at 6AM&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII) Trek to the top of Mullayanagiri via Sarpadaari route.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIII) Have Breakfast at the peak.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIV) Trek back down and return to homestay&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nV) Visit Belur Temple&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVI) ETA Bangalore 11:30 PM&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrek Distance:- 3 KM one way.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrek Difficulty:- Moderate to difficult&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEarly bird offer:- Rs.2599/-* (For First few bookings)&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nActual price:- 2899/-*&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe trip cost includes :&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Meals: 2 Breakfast; 2 Lunch; 2 Dinner.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Tent/dorm Stay on the 2nd September 2017.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Campfire and other activities. (Like it was last time around, it&amp;#39;s gonna involve a lot of fun).&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. First Aid kit in case of emergencies. (We hope we don&amp;#39;t have any).&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Trek Guide charges.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Forest entry charges.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExclusions:-&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTransportation &amp;amp; Fuel costs and other things not mentioned above.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNote:-&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1) People can make their own transportation arrangements or we could do that for you. The transportation arranged by us will INCUR ADDITIONAL CHARGES.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2) Accommodation will be on sharing basis.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3) We all will travel together from Bangalore immaterial of the mode of Transport.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe surroundings around the Home stay will make you feel very close to Nature.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe would like to reiterate &amp;amp; be understood that it is a no-frills nature retreat &amp;amp; not a luxury resort.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;For bookings and queries:-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Call or whatsapp us on&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;+91 890-443-3063&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;+91 953-815-7494&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','../images/event-images/1485949287_akhil_post_2.jpg,../images/event-images/Belur03.jpg','','','','','','chikmagalur','2017-08-07 05:26:39',1,1),(4,'Test','2345','2017-08-09','2017-08-10','&lt;p&gt;test&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;test&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;test&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','../images/event-images/1485949287_akhil_post_2.jpg,../images/event-images/Belur03.jpg','','','','','','test','2017-08-07 05:38:38',1,1),(5,'Coorg Adventures','3799','2017-10-07','2017-10-08','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;It&amp;#39;s not the mountain that we conquer but ourselves.&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: