: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;This sleepy little beach town has the look and the feel of a place unhindered by the whirlwind progress of modern society and technology. This is a place, unaware of the concept of time and routine. Everything in the town lends to the laid-back, rustic air. One gets off the bus, and comes face to face with warm, smiling visages, tanned ripe in the sun &amp;ndash; friendly locals and foreign nationals who managed to get similarly drawn into the timeless state of being that is Gokarna.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;So then what do we have in store for you?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;It is going to be a 2 days 2 Nights Event.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; fon