 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;3.All cancellation requests made 5 days prior or on the day of the event, no refund will be made.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','../images/event-images/22780512_1947777818773066_7422392353001756414_n.jpg','','','','','','kodachadri-trekkers-paradise','2017-11-01 16:41:51',0,1),(9,'Agumbe - Gokarna : West Coast Adventures','6000','2017-12-22','2017-12-25','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Monks on Wheels brings you their ultimate event so you could Get the best of both worlds! As we take you on a 3N/4D unbelievable tour through the thick jungles of western ghats and thrilling strips of the west coast of Karnataka. This is one event where even the journey matters.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;A jungle camp and a beach camp! Sounds exciting isn&amp;#39;t it? That is not all! We will also stay at the place where the Malgudi days Tv series was shot. This along with a visit to a hidden waterfall, beautiful view of the sunset, a ride along the sea side and Monks on Wheels will give you an experience worth cherishing for a life time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Book your tickets at&amp;nbsp; :-&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://go.eventshigh.com/37ytx&quot;&gt;http://go.eventshigh.com/37ytx&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Let us quickly get into the details of the event.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Itinerary for the Event:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Day 1 (22nd Dec 2017)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;I)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;text_exposed_show&quot; style=&quot;display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Depart from Bengaluru at 5:30 AM and have Breakfast en route.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII) Visit the old ruins of Shettihalli Church.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIII) Continue the journey, have lunch on enroute.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIV) Later reach the home stay at Agumbe and visit the beautiful &amp;quot;Sunset point&amp;quot; in the evening ( if time permits) , Have Dinner at the Nostalgic Malgudi Days home and overnight stay.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNote:- Accommodation on sharing basis&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDay 2 (23rd Dec 2017)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI) Wake up early morning to freshen up, Have breakfast and leave for the jungle camp site.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII) Reach the camp site, carry packed lunch and start for the hidden Koodluteertha Falls.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIII) Trek inside the thick forest, Enjoy and play in magnificent Koodlueertha waterfalls.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIV) Have packed lunch and return to the campsite and have campfire followed by Bonfire dinner and tent stay.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDay3 (24th Dec 2017)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI) Again we wake up early, freshen up have breakfast and start the journey to Gokarna&lt;br /&gt;\r\n.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII) Reach Gokarna Beach and have lunch in the homestay.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIII) Relax till evening and start the beach trail from Gokarna beach to Kudle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIV) Enjoy the outstanding view at Jatayu Theertha and return back to homestay.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nV) Once back, get ready to soak yourselves in rain dance followed by campfire party, dinner and overnight stay in tents on the beach.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDay 4 (25th Dec 2017)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI) Have an early Morning dip in the beach.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII) Later freshen up, have breakfast and start the return journey to Bengaluru.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIII) We&amp;#39;ll be having lunch and dinner on the way back to the city.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRoute: Bengaluru -&amp;gt; Shettihalli Church -&amp;gt; Agumbe -&amp;gt; Koodlutheertha Falls -&amp;gt; Agumbe -&amp;gt; Gokarna -&amp;gt; Bengaluru&lt;br /&gt;\r\nApprox Ride Distance: 1300 KM&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nActual Cost: Rs.6399/-* (inclusive of Taxes)&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEarly Bird Offer: Rs.5599/-* (Inclusive of taxes)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe trip cost includes :&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Delicious Meals on all the days!&lt;br /&gt;\r\na) Breakfast on Day 1, 2, 3 &amp;amp; 4&lt;br /&gt;\r\nb) Lunch on Day 1, 2, 3 &amp;amp; 4&lt;br /&gt;\r\nc) Dinner on Day 1, 2, 3 &amp;amp; 4&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Accommodation&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\na) Day 1: Dorm Stay in the Historic 100 year old house of magudi days.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nb) Day 2: Tent stay inside the jungle.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nc) Day 3: Tent stay on the beach.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Campfire under a million stars on 2 days.(if weather permits)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. All the activities mentioned in the itinerary are included in the package.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Forest entry charges.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. First Aid kit in case of emergencies. (We hope we don&amp;#39;t have any)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. A dedicated Team member from Monks on Wheels with you throughout the journey.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExclusions:-&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTransportation &amp;amp; Fuel costs and other things not mentioned above.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNote:-&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1) People can make their own transportation arrangements or we could do that for you. The transportation arranged by us will INCUR ADDITIONAL CHARGES.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2) We need a minimum of 10 people or the event might be cancelled with full refund.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3) We need a minimum of 5 bikes to organize a bike ride or else they have to reach the location provided by us on their own at the mentioned time.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4) Accommodation will be on sharing basis.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe surroundings around the Home stay will make you feel very close to Nature.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe would like to reiterate &amp;amp; be understood that it is a no-frills nature retreat &amp;amp; not a luxury resort.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThings required for the event :-&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. Water bottles&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Rain coat (in case it rains)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Torch&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Personal Medical kit&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Extra pair clothing&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. One cover sheet&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Carry bag&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. Jackets or sweaters&lt;br /&gt;\r\n9. Trek shoes (any shoes with good grip)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n10. Cap&lt;br /&gt;\r\n11. Umbrella&lt;br /&gt;\r\n12. Glucose&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor bookings and queries:-&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCall or whatsapp us on&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n+91 953-815-7494&lt;br /&gt;\r\n+91 903-610-4829&lt;br /&gt;\r\nor just send us a message on Facebook and we will connect with you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nRefund and Cancellation Policy:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1. If the notice is received more than 20 days prior to the event, 100% of the amount paid will be refunded.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. If the notice is received up to 20 days prior to the event, 50% of the amount paid shall be refunded.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3.All cancellation requests made 5 days prior or on the day of the event, no refund will be made&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;+91 953-815-7494&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: &amp;quot;SF Optimized&amp;quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &amp;quot;.SFNSText-Regular&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.12px;&quot;&gt;+91 890-443-3063&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','../images/event-images/agumbe.jpg','','','','','','agumbe-gokarna-west-coast-adventures','2017-12-16 10:02:12',0,1),(10,'Gokarna - Sea Sand Expedition','3499','2017-12-23','2017-12-25','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;GOKARNA!!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Does it even need an introduction?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;This sleepy little beach town has the look and the feel of a place unhindered by the whirlwind progress of modern society and technology. This is a place, unaware of the concept of time and routine. Everything in the town lends to the laid-back, rustic air. One gets off the bus, and comes face to face with warm, smiling visages, tanned ripe in the sun &amp;ndash; friendly locals and foreign nationals who managed to get similarly drawn into the timeless state of being that is Gokarna.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;So then what do we have in store for you?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;It is going to be a 2 days 1 Night Event.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The journey begins in the evening on Saturday and ends at night on Monday (christmas). The most important part&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;text_exposed_show&quot; style=&quot;display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;of the event is the beach trek.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe will be staying in tents by the beach.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe event is open to all kinds of travellers, so you may get your own bike, car or we could organise a suitable transport at additional cost.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Book your tickets at :-&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://go.eventshigh.com/e690h&quot;&gt;http://go.eventshigh.com/e690h&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Itinerary for the event:-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Day 0 (23rd Dec 2017)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Departure from Bengaluru around 9 PM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(People are requested to have light dinner before departure.)&lt;/spa